information: TOUS MOTEURS DIESEL is a specialized dealer with more than 30 years' experience reselling new and reconditioned diesel engines. You can find our wide selection of engine models suitable for all makes. Our products are geared to the needs of farming machinery and civil engineering machinery such as lift trucks and crane transporters. We undertake to find you the right engine, thanks to our network of trusted suppliers that we have consolidated over many years' trading. Furthermore, our team of experts can advise you on replacing your diesel engine. This is because we have more than 5000 items in stock and so can deliver to you in the fastest time at keen prices. We can also satisfy your needs for parts and in particular, can supply you with engine kits. Our engines come with a 6-month to 2-year warranty, depending on the make.
